From: Office Manager <officemanager@totalphysiomv.com>
Subject: Total Physio website assistance please!
Date: 15 February 2023 at 10:42:54 am AEDT
To: "chris@wolfiq.com.au" <chris@wolfiq.com.au>

Hi Chris,

I hope you are well.

I was wondering if you may be able to assist in the following updates please:

Update Team Photos:
Isabel Ferris (black t-shirt) please place under Physiotherapists. Her Bio is below.
Jessie Purvis - Admin team.

Isabel graduated with a Bachelor of Physiotherapy from the University of South Australia in 2016. She has worked in various parts of Sydney and also the UK. She uses a combination of hands on/manual therapy, dry needling, exercises and education with her patients. In some cases she will also treat patients using Mandarin.

She has a special interest in TMJ, neck, shoulder, back and perinatal MSK conditions.

In her spare time she enjoys going for walks, playing the piano and reading.

Updated class calendar
Would you mind updating this calendar on the website and the respective ones as you have done previously. It looks like you have linked them through and more complicated for me to work out!!

Hyperlinks
Could you please send me directions on how to hyperlink?

Womens and Mens Health page
We have decided that WMPH page needed a re-work and re-type to make it easier and to be more consistent with how the other pages are set out.
In blue is where there can be a hyperlink to the WMPH conditions page. Please see information attached.
The ultrasound video should stay on the bottom of the page.

Thank you Chris, please reach out if you have any questions.

Kind Regards,

Cindy
